name: An Angel Called Night
description:
"Lailah chooses a soul from the
Garden of Eden and commands it to
enter the embryo. Lailah watches
over the development in the womb
and shows the rewards and
punishments available to the
individual. Then right before birth,
Lailah strikes the newborn above the
lip, making it forget what was learned
and creating the philtrum. Lailah
serves as a guardian angel throughout
a person's life and at death, leads the
soul into the afterlife." 2400 x 3000
pixels. Original Music by parrott_ism
